     "text": [
      " ============feed back report================\n",
      "**Student Feedback Analysis Report**\n",
      "\n",
      "**Overall Student Sentiment:** Mixed\n",
      "\n",
      "The feedback suggests that students appreciated certain aspects of the course, such as clear explanations, hands-on coding sessions, and the overall quality of the course. However, there are also concerns about the pace of the lectures, lack of practical examples, and the difficulty of assignments.\n",
      "\n",
      "**Top 3 Strengths Mentioned:**\n",
      "\n",
